ot%20dead%20outside%20his%20son%20Zeeshan%20Siddique's%20office%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20East%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20three%20shooters%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20murder.%20Out%20of%20the%20three%2C%20two%20have%20been%20arrested%20-%20Gurmail%20Baljit%20Singh%2C%2023%2C%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Dharamraj%20Kashyap%2C%2019%2C%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20and%20the%20third%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Shiv%20Kumar%2C%20also%20from%20UP.%20A%20fourth%20person%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20handler%2C%20is%20also%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20which%20unfolded%20around%209%3A30%20pm%2C%20saw%20Mr%20Siddique%20and%20his%20associate%20targeted%20by%20assailants%20who%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%2C%20fatally%20striking%20the%20politician%20in%20the%20chest.%20Hours%20after%20the%20shooting%2C%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20assassination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-death-bjp-vs-congress-after-veteran-leader-baba-siddique-shot-dead-in-mumbai-6778568%5C%22%3EBJP%20vs%20Congress%20After%20Veteran%20Leader%20Baba%20Siddique%20Shot%20Dead%20In%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspects%20had%20been%20monitoring%20Mr%20Siddique%20for%20months%2C%20conducting%20reconnaissance%20of%20his%20residence%20and%20office%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20police%20revealed%20that%20the%20suspects%20had%20been%20paid%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20in%20advance%20for%20the%20hit%20and%20that%20arms%20had%20been%20delivered%20to%20them%20only%20days%20before%20the%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20arrested%20suspects%20are%20now%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20and%20the%20hunt%20for%20the%20others%20continues.%20Mumbai%20Police%20have%20also%20heightened%20the%20security%20around%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%20-%20the%20site%20at%20which%20a%20shooting%20incident%20took%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20April%2014%2C%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20neighbourhood%20was%20rocked%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20gunfire%20as%20two%20men%20on%20motorbikes%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence.%20The%20accused%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20were%20charged%20with%20conspiracy%20to%20murder%20and%20other%20grave%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20had%20issued%20a%20contract%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20assassinate%20the%20actor.%20The%20plan%20was%20hatched%20over%20several%20months%2C%20from%20August%202023%20to%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique%20enjoyed%20comradeship%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20therefore%2C%20his%20killing%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20with%20senior%20politicians%20offering%20condolences%20while%20expressing%20outrage%20over%20the%20escalating%20violence%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-death-strongman-to-bollywood-mediator-baba-siddique-beyond-lavish-iftar-parties-6777937%5C%22%3EStrongman%20To%20Bollywood%20Mediator%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%20Beyond%20Lavish%20Iftar%20Parties%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20react%2C%20calling%20Mr%20Siddique's%20murder%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20beyond%20words.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20tragic%20demise%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Minister%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20is%20shocking%20beyond%20words.%20In%20this%20hour%20of%20grief%2C%20I%20offer%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20supporters.%20Justice%20must%20be%20en