law%20and%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique%2C%2066%2C%20a%20prominent%20political%20figure%20known%20for%20his%20three-time%20stint%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20Bandra%20West%2C%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20unknown%20attackers%20outside%20his%20son%20Zeeshan%20Siddique's%20office%20in%20Bandra%20East%20last%20night.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Mr%20Siddique%20sustained%20multiple%20gunshot%20wounds%2C%20including%20one%20to%20the%20chest%2C%20and%20died%20of%20his%20injuries%20at%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20later%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-shooters-claim-they-were-from-bishnoi-gang-sources-6777286%5C%22%3EBaba%20Siddique%20Shooters%20Claim%20To%20Be%20From%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20Gang%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20murder%2C%20Mumbai%20Police%20arrested%20two%20suspects%20who%20claimed%20to%20belong%20to%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20Bishnoi%2C%20incarcerated%20at%20Gujarat's%20Sabarmati%20jail%2C%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20shooting%20incident%20outside%20the%20residence%20of%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20known%20to%20have%20been%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Mr%20Siddique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Slugfest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tragic%20demise%20of%20Baba%20Siddique%20ji%20is%20shocking%20and%20saddening.%20My%20thoughts%20are%20with%20his%20family%20in%20this%20difficult%20time.%20This%20horrifying%20incident%20exposes%20the%20complete%20collapse%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20government%20must%20take%20responsibility%2C%20and%20justice%20must%20prevail%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20echoed%20similar%20sentiments%2C%20calling%20Mr%20Siddique's%20murder%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20beyond%20words.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20tragic%20demise%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Minister%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20is%20shocking%20beyond%20words.%20In%20this%20hour%20of%20grief%2C%20I%20offer%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20supporters.%20Justice%20must%20be%20ensured%2C%20and%20the%20present%20Maharashtra%20government%20must%20order%20a%20thorough%20and%20transparent%20investigation.%20The%20culprits%20must%20be%20brought%20to%20book%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Accountability%20is%20paramount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-death-strongman-to-bollywood-mediator-baba-siddique-beyond-lavish-iftar-parties-6777937%5C%22%3EStrongman%20To%20Bollywood%20Mediator%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%20Beyond%20Lavish%20Iftar%20Parties%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20news%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20senior%20Maharashtra%20leader%20Baba%20Siddiqui%20is%20extremely%20sad.%20I%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20give%20the%20deceased%20a%20high%20place%20in%20heaven%20and%20give%20patience%20and%20courage%20to%20the%20family.%20What%20name%20will%20you%20give%20to%20such%20criminal%20incidents%20that%20are%20continuously%20happening%20in%20Maharashtra%20under%20the%20NDA%20rule%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Pradeep%20Bhandari%20said%20that%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20Alliance%20-%20comprising%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)%2C%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20or%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20faction)%20-%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20cracking%20down%20on%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NDA%20gove