al%20victory%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20Bandra%20West%20in%201999%2C%20a%20seat%20he%20successfully%20defended%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-ex-minister-baba-siddique-shot-at-in-mumbai-6775514%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20Ex%20Minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20Shot%20Dead%20Near%20Son's%20Office%20In%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique's%20tenure%20as%20Maharashtra's%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Food%20%26amp%3B%20Civil%20Supplies%2C%20Labour%2C%20FDA%2C%20and%20Consumer%20Protection%20from%202004%20to%202008%20solidified%20his%20reputation%20as%20an%20able%20administrator%20and%20a%20staunch%20advocate%20for%20communal%20harmony.%20His%20political%20manoeuvring%20was%20not%20confined%20to%20legislative%20chambers%3B%20he%20was%20equally%20adept%20at%20navigating%20Bollywood's%20intricate%20dynamics%2C%20earning%20admiration%20for%20his%20role%20in%20reconciling%20the%20infamous%20feud%20between%20superstars%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Salman%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBollywood%20Connections%20And%20Iftar%20Legacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique%20was%20a%20familiar%20face%20in%20Mumbai's%20entertainment%20circles%2C%20renowned%20for%20hosting%20lavish%20Iftar%20parties%20that%20brought%20together%20luminaries%20from%20both%20politics%20and%20Bollywood.%20These%20gatherings%20became%20iconic%20for%20their%20ability%20to%20transcend%20social%20barriers%2C%20uniting%20many%20of%20diverse%20backgrounds%20and%20some%20who%20carried%20longstanding%20grudges%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20event%20in%202013%20became%20the%20stuff%20of%20legend%20as%20Mr%20Siddique%20orchestrated%20a%20reunion%20between%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20who%20had%20drifted%20apart%20following%20a%20highly%20sensationalized%20rift.%20At%20the%20height%20of%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20stars%2C%20Mr%20Siddique%20strategically%20seated%20Shah%20Rukh%20next%20to%20Salman's%20father%2C%20the%20legendary%20screenwriter%20Salim%20Khan%2C%20during%20his%20Iftar%20party.%20The%20symbolic%20gesture%20thawed%20the%20icy%20relations%20and%20restored%20camaraderie%20between%20Bollywood's%20two%20biggest%20stars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-shooters-claim-they-were-from-bishnoi-gang-sources-6777286%5C%22%3EBaba%20Siddique%20Shooters%20Claim%20To%20Be%20From%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20Gang%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique's%20neighbours%20in%20Mumbai%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20former%20minister%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20polite%26quot%3B%20but%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Btough%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20Mr%20Siddique%20was%20rushed%20to%20Mumbai's%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20which%20quickly%20became%20a%20hotspot%20for%20Bollywood's%20who's%20who.%20Actors%20including%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Sanjay%20Dutt%20and%20Shilpa%20Shetty%2C%20among%20others%20were%20seen%20reaching%20the%20hospital%20to%20meet%20the%20family%20of%20the%20former%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Shift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20decades%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Siddique%20dropped%20a%20shocker%20and%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20party%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons%20for%20his%20departure%2C%20and%20joined%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%20However%2C%20Mr%20Siddique's%20ambitions%20faced%20hurdles%2C%20including%20legal%20challenges%20stemming%20from%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20investigation%20into%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20slum%20rehabilitation%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20journey%20was%20with%20Indira%20Gandhi-Rajiv%20Gandhi-Sanjay%20Gandhi.%20The%20current%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20is%20like%20my%20father.%20But%20sometimes%20some%20decisions%20have%20to%20be%20made%20in%20personal%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Siddique%20had%20said%20before%20joining%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Reactions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique%20enjoyed%20comradeship%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20therefore%2C%20his%20killing%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20with%20senior%20politicians%20offering%20condolences%20while%20expressing%20outrage%20over%20the%20escalating%20violence%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20react%2C%20calling%20Mr%20Siddique's%20murder%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20beyond%20words.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20tragic%20demise%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Minister%2C%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20is%20shocking%20beyond%20words.%20In%20this%20hour%20of%20grief%2C%20I%20offer%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20supporters.%20Justice%20must%20be%20ensured%2C%20and%20the%20present%20Maharashtra%20government%20must%20order%20a%20thorough%20and%20transparent%20investigation.%20The%20culprits%20must%20be%20brought%20to%20book%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Accountability%20is%20paramount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-ajit-pawar-faction-leader-shot-at-in-mumbai-6775628%5C%22%3EAll%20About%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Faction%20Leader%20Shot%20Dead%20In%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20expressed%20similar%20sentiments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tragic%20demise%20of%20Baba%20Siddique%20ji%20is%20shocking%20and%20saddening.%20My%20thoughts%20are%20with%20his%20family%20in%20this%20difficult%20time.%20This%20horrifying%20incident%20exposes%20the%20complete%20collapse%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20government%20must%20take%20responsibility%2C%20and%20justice%20must%20prevail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wrote%20about%20his%20former%20colleague%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripple%20effects%20of%20Mr%20Siddique's%20assassination%20reached%20beyond%20Maharashtra.%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(HAM)%2C%20expressed%20sorrow%20over%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20fellow%20leader%20with%20roots%20in%20Bihar.%20%26quot%3BThe%20news%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20Baba%20Siddiqui%2C%20one%20of%20the%20tall%20leaders%20of%20NCP%2C%20who%20hailed%20from%20Bihar%2C%20is%20very%20saddening%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Manjhi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20lively%20person.%20We%20request%20the%20Almighty%20to%20grant%20him%20a%20high%20place%20in%20his%20abode%20and%20grant%20patience%20to%20his%20loved%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20Chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20joined%20the%20chorus%20of%20condemnation.%20In%20his%20post%2C%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBaba%20Siddique's%20murder%20is%20highly%20condemnable.%20It%20reflects%20the%20deteriorating%20state%20of%20law%20%26amp%3B%20order%20in%20Maharashtra.%20May%20Allah%20grant%20him%20maghfirah.%20My%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%20friends%20%26amp%3B%20colleagues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20NCP%2C%20Mr%20Siddique's%20murder%20has%20prompted%20the%20cancellation%20of%20all%20scheduled%20party%20events.%20In%20a%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20the%20NCP%20announced%2C%20%26quot%3BKeeping%20in%20view%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20our%20party%20colleague%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20all%20party%20programmes%20for%20October%2013%2C%202024%20(Sunday)