ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-ajit-pawar-faction-leader-shot-at-in-mumbai-6775628%5C%22%3EMr%20Siddique%3C%2Fa%3E%20near%20his%20son's%20office%20and%20four%20hit%20him%20in%20the%20chest.%20Cops%2C%20who%20suspect%20it%20to%20be%20a%20contract%20killing%2C%20have%20formed%20four%20special%20teams%20to%20probe%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%2C%20that%20coincided%20with%20Dussehra%20festivities%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20three%20men.%20Two%20men%20-%20Gurmail%20Baljit%20Singh%2C%2023%2C%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Dharamraj%20Kashyap%2C%2019%2C%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20were%20arrested%20while%20the%20third%20remains%20on%20the%20run.%20Cops%2C%20however%2C%20believe%20someone%20else%20was%20providing%20them%20with%20information%20about%20Mr%20Siddique's%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20interrogation%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20Crime%20Branch%2C%20the%20two%20arrested%20suspects%20claimed%20they%20had%20been%20conducting%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20shooting%20spot%20in%20Bandra%20East%20for%20nearly%20a%20month%2C%20said%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20accused%20arrived%20there%20in%20an%20auto%20rickshaw%20last%20night%20and%20waited%20for%20a%20while%20before%20the%20shooting%20took%20place%2C%20added%20the%20sources%20in%20the%20crime%20branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20are%20probing%20the%20case%20from%20two%20angles%20-%20one%20involving%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20and%20another%20related%20to%20a%20slum%20rehabilitation%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20involvement%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20is%20suspected%20due%20to%20Mr%20Siddique's%20proximity%20to%20Bollywood%20star%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20who%20had%20received%20threats%20from%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi.%20Sources%20close%20to%20the%20victim%20claim%20he%20had%20received%20a%20death%20threat%2015%20days%20ago%20and%20was%20given%20the%20%E2%80%98Y'%20category%20security%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Siddique%2C%20however%2C%20did