ater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20just%20two%20months%20back%20the%20two%20got%20married%20and%20with%20the%20three-day%20Puja%20holidays%20beginning%2C%20Karthik%2C%20who%20works%20at%20the%20state-run%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20while%20Vismaya%20is%20a%20student%20in%20agriculture%2C%20had%20taken%20leave%20to%20go%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20driving%20from%20Kottarakara%20-%20the%20home%20town%20of%20Vismaya%20-%20to%20Aluva%20from%20where%20Karthik%20hails%20when%20the%20accident%20occurred%20near%20Kolencherry%20in%20Ernakulam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20IANS%2C%20Karthik%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20driving%20from%20her%20home%20town%20to%20mine%20at%20Aluva.%20This%20accident%20took%20place%20when%20our%20car%20lost%20control%20after%20hitting%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20road%2C%20moved%20off%20the%20road%2C%20hit%20a%20panchayat%20well%20on%20the%20roadside%2C%20broke%20its%20side%20walls%20and%20plunged%20into%20the%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyewitness%20Chakkapan%20said%20that%20it%20was%20around%209.20%20p.m.%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20%26quot%3BThe%20place%20is%20a%20crossroad%20and%20there%20is%20a%20big%20dip...%20the%20young%20couple's%20vehicle%20lost%20control%20when%20they%20could%20not%20identify%20the%20dip%20because%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20water.%20The%20car%20then%20moved%20forward%20as%20it%20went%20out%20of%20control%20and%20hit%20the%20side%20wall%20of%20the%20well%20about%2030%20meters%20from%20the%20dip%20and%20fell%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoon%20hearing%20the%20sound%2C%20those%20standing%20in%20and%20around%20the%20junction%20came%20running%20and%20the%20rescue%20began%2C%26quot%3B%20Chakkapan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20local%2C%20Mary%20and%20her%20son%20came%20running%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20she%20went%20back%20and%20got%20a%20ladder.%20%26quot%3BWe%