ir%2C%20Surya%20Factor%20Behind%20T20I%20Ton%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20someone%20whose%20immense%20talent%20hasn't%20really%20blossomed%20at%20the%20international%20stage%20on%20a%20consistent%20basis%20so%20far%2C%20Sanju%20Samson%20was%20on%20Saturday%20a%20relieved%20man%20after%20hitting%20his%20maiden%20T20I%20ton%20in%20the%20third%20game%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20but%20conceded%20he%20too%20has%20felt%20he%20%26quot%3Bcan%20do%20much%20better%26quot%3B.%20Samson%20hammered%20eight%20sixes%20and%2011%20fours%20to%20make%20111%20off%20only%2047%20balls%20while%20also%20recording%20the%20second-fastest%20T20I%20ton%20by%20an%20Indian%20--%20off%20just%2040%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamson's%20ton%20powered%20India%20to%20a%20record%20total%20of%20297%2F6%2C%20their%20highest-ever%20in%20the%20format%20and%20second%20highest%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(I%20am)%20very%20happy%20that%20they%20(teammates)%20are%20happy%20I%20did%20well.%20It%20can%20get%20frustrating%20knowing%20what%20you%20can%20do%20out%20there%2C%20and%20I%20have%20also%20felt%20I%20can%20do%20much%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20during%20the%20presentation%20ceremony%20after%20India's%203-0%20series%20win%20with%20a%20133-run%20hammering%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20third%20and%20final%20T20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20with%20playing%20so%20many%20games%20I%20know%20how%20do%20deal%20with%20pressure%20and%20my%20failures%20because%20I%20have%20failed%20a%20lot.%20Just%20focus%20was%20on%20process%20and%20knowing%20you%20will%20do%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlaying%20for%20your%20country%2C%20that%20pressure%20was%20there%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20perform%20and%20wanted%20to%20show.%20But%20I%20still%20kept%20it%20basic%20and%20wanted%20to%20take%20it%20by%20one%20ball%20(at%20a%20time).%26quot%3B%20Samson%20said%20he%20has%20got%20the%20full%20backing%20of%20the%20team%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20leadership%20tells%20me%20they%20back%20me%20no%20matter%20what...%20not%20just%20in%20words%20but%20in%20actions%20also.%20Last%20series%20I%20got%20two%20ducks%20and%20went%20back%20to%20Kerala%20thinking%20what%20will%20happen%2C%20but%20I'm%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20named%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Series%20for%20his%20impactful%20batting%20performances%2C%20credited%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20skipper%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20for%20his%20impressive%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20kind%20of%20freedom%20skipper%20and%20coach%20have%20given%20is%20fantastic%20for%20the%20whole%20group.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20if%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20sport%20you%20can%20get%20the%20maximum%20out%20of%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20said%20the%20emphasis%20has%20been%20on%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%9Cselfless%E2%80%9D%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(I)%20wanted%20to%20have%20selfless%20cricketers%20and%20want%20to%20be%20a%20selfless%20team%2C%20enjoy%20each%20others'%20performances.%20That%20camaraderie%20is%20coming%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGauti%20bhai%20(Gautam%20Gambhir)%20said%20the%20same%20thing%20before%20the%20series%20that%20no%20one%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20team%2C%20no%20matter%20you%20are%20on%2049%20or%2099%2C%20you%20have%20to%20hit%20the%20ball%20out%20of%20the%20field.%20That's%20what%20Sanju%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suryakumar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20spinner%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20completed%2050%20wickets%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%2C%20said%20there%20is%20a%20healthy%20competition%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHealthy%20competition%20is%20good%20pressure.%20I%20wasn't%20under%20pressure%20but%20didn't%20want%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20opportunity%20given%20tonight%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELosing%20captain%20Najmul%20Hossain%20Shanto%20said%20Bang