0legacy%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20mentoring%20and%20developing%20the%20modern%20business%20leadership%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Mr%20Tata%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20cared%20about%20making%20India%20better.%20Deep%20condolences%20to%20his%20loved%20ones%20and%20Rest%20in%20Peace%20Shri%20Ratan%20Tata%20Ji%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBill%20Gates%20too%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20on%20the%20death%20of%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bvisionary%20leader%20whose%20dedication%20to%20improving%20lives%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20India%20-%20and%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20LinkedIn%20Post%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20recalled%20meeting%20Mr%20Tata%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20and%20expressed%20his%20admiration%20for%20the%20business%20tycoon's%20commitment%20to%20improving%20lives.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20always%20moved%20by%20his%20strong%20sense%20of%20purpose%20and%20service%20to%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gates%20wrote%20in%20his%20post.%20He%20also%20recalled%20collaborating%20with%20Mr%20Tata%20on%20several%20initiatives%20and%20said%20that%20his%20legacy%20will%20inspire%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRatan%20Tata%20was%20a%20visionary%20leader%20whose%20dedication%20to%20improving%20lives%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20India-and%20the%20world.%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20meeting%20him%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20and%20I%20was%20always%20moved%20by%20his%20strong%20sense%20of%20purpose%20and%20service%20to%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gates%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTogether%2C%20we%20partnered%20on%20numerous%20initiatives%20to%20help%20people%20lead%20healthier%2C%20more%20prosperous%20lives.%20His%20loss%20will%20be%20felt%20around%20the%20world%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20but%20I%20know%20the%20legacy%20he%20left%20and%20example%20he%20set%20will%20continue%20to%20inspire%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C