ficiencies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Arumugavelu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20it's%20implementing%20the%20tech%20is%20by%20using%20AI%20computer%20vision%2C%20which%20allows%20computers%20to%20analyze%20and%20identify%20subjects%20in%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20for%20geospatial%20intelligent%20cell%20site%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20figure%20out%20where%20to%20densify%20our%20network%20and%20do%20it%20effectively%20and%20efficiently%2C%20AI%20also%20helps%20us%20achieve%20energy%20optimization%20and%20facilitate%20predictive%20maintenance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerizon%20is%20also%20building%20a%20fully%20automated%20supply%20chain%20digital%20twin%2C%20which%20helps%20with%20monitoring%20inventory%20levels%2C%20Arumugavelu%20said%2C%20and%20using%20AI%20in%20workforce%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20predictive%20market%20demand%2C%20we%20can%20proactively%20address%20staffing%20levels%20within%20our%20distribution%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20includes%20management%20of%20our%20stores%2C%20call%20centers%2C%20and%20also%20identifying%20where%20to%20start%20technicians%20in%20the%20field.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20consumer-facing%20implementation%20of%20AI%20is%20the%20oft-maligned%20digital%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-customer-service-morgan-stanley-interns-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20service%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20AI%20implemented%20across%20each%20step%20before%20a%20customer%20even%20places%20a%20call%2C%20we%20can%20determine%20where%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20contact%20us%2C%20predict%20what%20they%20may%20need%2C%20and%20specify%20the%20next%20best%20action%20or%20offer%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Arumugavelu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20customer%20needs%20advanced%20support%2C%20the%20system%20draws%20on%20%26quot%3BAI-enabled%20intelligent%20agent%20pair