4-e74095fbc3b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20realized%20our%20cultural%20differences%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20grew%20closer%2C%20we%20realized%20how%20different%20we%20were%2C%20leading%20us%20to%20have%20some%20deep%20and%20intense%20conversations.%20My%20upbringing%20in%20Punjabi%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%20vibrant%20traditions%2C%20music%2C%20and%20cuisine%20%E2%80%94%20contrasts%20sharply%20with%20Katy's%20American%20experience.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcultural-differences-between-us-europe-american-traveler-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20feels%20less%20rooted%20to%20her%2C%20Katy%20appreciates%20Indian%20food%20and%20is%20eager%20to%20learn%20Punjabi%2C%20encouraging%20me%20to%20speak%20it%20more.%20This%20mutual%20respect%20for%20each%20other's%20cultures%20has%20eased%20our%20blending%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20our%20shared%20enthusiasm%20for%20each%20other's%20traditions%2C%20we've%20faced%20challenges%20with%20the%20smaller%20details.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-back-to-india-after-living-abroad-for-decade-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20common%20to%20stay%20with%20one's%20parents%20until%20marriage%2C%20while%20in%20American%20culture%2C%20independence%20is%20often%20encouraged%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20This%20difference%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20admire%20Katy's%20resilience%20and%20independence%20%E2%80%94%20qualities%20I%20deeply%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kaajal%20Nanda%20and%20her%20wife%20in%20their%20wedding%20dresses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67042b513f2165d716def291%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221367%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20left%2C%20blended%20her%20Hindu%20heritag