%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20lettuce%20for%20serving.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20combination%20of%20ingredients%20was%20outside%20my%20standard-burger%20comfort%20zone.%20Still%2C%20I%20gathered%20everything%20and%20did%20the%20necessary%20prep%20work%2C%20like%20draining%20the%20canned%20chiles%2C%20slicing%20the%20tomato%2C%20and%20chopping%20the%20cilantro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20prepared%20the%20burgers%20exactly%20as%20instructed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223191%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20bowl%20of%20ground%20chicken%20with%20pieces%20of%20cilantro%2C%20green%20chiles%2C%20and%20seasonings%20that%20need%20to%20be%20mixed%20in%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670808ffa70318649280eabd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222393%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20mixed%20all%20the%20burger%20ingredients%20together%20in%20a%20bowl.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20recipe%20was%20accompanied%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marthastewart.com%2F1153985%2Fgreen-chile-chicken-burgers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk-through%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Stewart's%20website%2C%20so%20I%20watched%20it%20to%20see%20if%20there%20were%20any%20helpful%20tips%20I%20could%20pick%20up%20before%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chef%20in%20the%20video%20said%20the%20raw%20patties%20were%20very%20delicate%2C%20so%20I%20started%20to%20get%20nervous%20that%20my%20burgers%20would%20fall%20apart%20before%20they%20reached%20the%20grill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20did%20exactly%20what%20she%20suggested.%20I%20drained%20the%20green%20chiles%20well%2C%20mixed%20the%20ingredients%20together%2C%20formed%20patties%2C%20and%20chilled%20the%20raw%20burgers%20in%20the%20refrigerator%20to%20firm%20them%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20about%20an%20hour%2C%20I%20removed%20the%20burger%20patties%20from%20the%20refrigerator.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223309%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20four%20raw%20burger%20patties%20with%20pieces%20of%20cilantro%20and%20green%20chiles%20with%20juices%20seeping%20out%20of%20the%20patties%20onto%20the%20plate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67080937a70318649280ead3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222482%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20after%20an%20hour%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20the%20green-chile%20chicken%20burgers%20seemed%20very%20wet.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20took%20them%20out%20of%20the%20fridge%2C%20the%20plate%20was%20covered%20in%20liquid%20that%20had%20seeped%20out%20of%20the%20burgers%20while%20they%20chilled.%20The%20patties%20themselves%20looked%20crumbly%20and%20wet%20and%20fell%20apart%20when%20I%20touched%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20draining%20the%20juices%20in%20my%20sink%2C%20I%20tried%20refrigerating%20the%20patties%20for%20another%20hour%20in%20hopes%20of%20seeing%20them%20firm%20up.%20However%2C%20even%20after%20two%20hours%20of%20chill%20time%2C%20the%20burgers%20remained%20wet%20and%20mushy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGrilling%20these%20chicken%20burgers%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20task.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223385%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20burger%20patties%20on%20a%20red-hot%20indoor%20grill%20with%20visible%20pieces%20of%20cilantro%20and%20green%20chiles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6708099c3f2165d716dfeb3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222539%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20green-chile%20chicken%20burgers%20didn't%20hold%20together%20well%20when%20I%20tried%20grilling%20them.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20grill%20the%20patties%2C%20my%20precautions%20seemed%20to%20have%20done%20little%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20picked%20up%20the%20burgers%20from%20the%20plate%2C%20they%20started%20falling%20apart%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20re-form%20the%20patties.%20Following%20the%20directions%20from%20the%20video%2C%20I%20spread%20oil%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20each%20one%20before%20dropping%20it%20onto%20the%20grill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20let%20the%20burgers%20cook%20for%20about%20five%20minutes%20on%20each%20side.%20When%20it%20was%20time%20to%20flip%20them%2C%20two%20out%20of%20four%20patties%20fell%20apart%20completely%2C%20and%20the%20other%20two%20lost%20pieces%20of%20meat%20here%20and%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2010%20minutes%20on%20the%20grill%2C%20the%20burgers%20reached%20an%20internal%20temperature%20of%20165%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20a%20signal%20that%20the%20chicken%20had%20cooked%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20instructions%20for%20grilling%20the%20tomato%20slices%20and%20buns%20seemed%20a%20bit%20off.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223427%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20cooked%20burger%20patties%20with%20visible%20pieces%20of%20cilantro%20and%20green%20chiles%20and%20cooked%20pieces%20of%20tomatoes%20on%20the%20palte%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67080a0ea70318649280eb22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20think%20some%20of%20the%20burger%20toppings%2C%20like%20the%20tomato%20slices%2C%20needed%20more%20time%20on%20the%20grill.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20prepare%20the%20toppings.%20I%20followed%20the%20suggested%20two-minute%20grill%20time%20for%20the%20sliced%20tomatoes%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20they%20didn't%20get%20the%20dark%2C%20caramelized%20grill%20marks%20I'd%20have%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heat%20time%20for%20the%20sesame%20buns%20also%20seemed%20off%20to%20me.%20The%20recipe%20said%20they'd%20only%20need%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20grill%20for%20about%20a%20minute%2C%20but%20this%20wasn't%20enough%20time%20to%20fully%20heat%20the%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20buns%20got%20warm%20and%20toasty%2C%20I%20think%20they%20needed%20another%20minute%20or%20two%20on%20the%20grill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20burgers%20looked%20beautiful%2C%20and%20one%20condiment%20was%20surprisingly%20good.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20burgers%20with%20pieces%20of%20green%20chiles%20and%20cilantro%20on%20buns%20with%20sour%20cream%2C%20tomato%20slices%2C%20and%20lettuce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67080a3d3f2165d716dfeb66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20flavor%20the%20sour%20cream%20gave%20to%20the%20burgers.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20plate%20Stewart's%20burgers%2C%20I%20stacked%20a%20dollop%20of%20sour%20cream%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20Dijon%20mustard%2C%20a%20patty%2C%20a%20tomato%20slice%2C%20and%20a%20lettuce%20leaf%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-store-bought-burger-buns-better-according-to-chefs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esesame%20bun%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20fully%20assembled%20burger%20looked%20colorful%20and%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20took%20a%20bite%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20delicious%20the%20sour%20cream%20was%20as%20a%20burger%20condiment.%20The%20tartness%20of%20the%20creamy%20topping%20cut%20through%20the%20slight%20spice%20of%20the%20cumin%20and%20chile%20and%20ended%20up%20being%20my%20family's%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20burgers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20thought%20the%20patties%20themselves%20tasted%20like%20they%20should've%20been%20part%20of%20a%20taco-night%20menu%20instead.%20The%20chicken%20patties%2C%20rich%20with%20earthy%20green%20chiles%2C%20cumin%2C%20and%20fresh%20cilantro%2C%20had%20a%20unique%20flavor%20profile%20that%20wasn't%20anyone%20at%20my%20table's%20favorite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20I%20made%20these%20burgers%20again%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20differently.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20Terri%20Peters%20wearing%20a%20pink%20and%20blue%20flannel%20and%20holding%20a%20plate%20of%20burgers%20with%20pieces%20of%20green%20chiles%20and%20cilantro%20on%20buns%20with%20sour%20cream%2C%20tomato%20slices%2C%20and%20lettuce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67080a7fa70318649280eb3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20family%20didn't%20love%20these%20burgers%2C%20though%20they%20looked%20beautiful.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20like%20many%20parts%20of%20this%20recipe%2C%20from%20the%20fall-apart%20chicken-burger%20mixture%20to%20the%20under-heated%20sesame%20buns.%20Still%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20sat%20at%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20puzzling%20over%20what%20we%20could%20do%20differently%20to%20improve%20the%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20attempted%20these%20burgers%20again%2C%20I'd%20add%20eggs%20and%20breadcrumbs%20to%20the%20ground-chicken%20mixture%20to%20help%20the%20patties%20stay%20together%20better.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20add%20a%20sharp-cheddar%20cheese%20to%20the%20mix%2C%20which%20might%20help%20balance%20the%20acidity%20of%20the%20sour%20cream%2C%20mustard%2C%20chiles%2C%20and%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-simple-chile-chicken-burgers-review-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728737162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67080b9ea70318649280ebb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-simple-chile-chicken-burgers-review-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2