t%20history%20says%20about%20the%20bull%20market's%20future%20as%20it%20enters%20its%20third%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287e38ea9-e2ca-4929-9a94-031a99caf946%5C%22%3EFreedom%20Capital%20Markets%2C%20Jay%20Woods%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20global%20strategist%20Jay%20Woods%20of%20Freedom%20Capital%20Markets%20said%20what's%20most%20telling%20about%20the%20current%20bull%20market%20is%20that%20very%20few%20believed%20in%20it%20in%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20preface%20it%20with%20when%20it%20started%2C%20no%20one%20believed%20it.%20They%20just%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20bear%20market%20rally.%20And%20then%20they%20doubted%20that%20it%20had%20legs%2C%20and%20then%20it%20was%20just%20seven%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Woods%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20it%20is%20powerful.%20And%20I%20think%20the%20momentum%20is%20continuing.%20You%20got%20the%20rate%20cycle%2C%20you%20got%20broadening%20out%2C%20we%20have%20wind%20at%20our%20sails%2C%20and%20this%20bull%20market%20should%20last%20at%20least%20another%2012%2C%20maybe%2018%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoods%20said%20he%20is%20encouraged%20that%20market%20leadership%20is%20diverse%20and%20no%20longer%20concentrated%20in%20mega-cap%20technology%20companies.%20A%20recent%20example%20is%20the%20rotation%20into%20utility%20stocks%2C%20which%20have%20surged%20on%20the%20AI%20power%20demand%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20Wall%20Street%20expression%20is%20%26quot%3Brotation%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20a%20bull%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20appears%20to%20be%20playing%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20to%20look%20back%20and%20celebrate%20two%20years%2C%20but%20it%20still%20feels%20like%20the%20party%20is%20just%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20Woods%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222275e95f-cb77-497d-97ee-938609a82fa6%5C%22%3ECarson%20Group%2C%20Ryan%20Detrick%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Carson%20Group%20chief%20market%20strategist%20Ryan%20Detrick%2C%20the%20bull%20market%20in%20stocks%20is%20still%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20many%20might%20think%20this%20bull%20market%20has%20gone%20too%20far%20and%20is%20getting%20old%2C%20that%20isn't%20the%20case%20at%20all.%20If%20you%20look%20back%20at%20history%2C%20bull%20markets%20last%20more%20than%20five%20years%20on%20average%2C%20making%20this%20one%20at%20two%20years%20actually%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20Detrick%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetrick%20said%20that%20while%20he%20sees%20more%20gains%20ahead%2C%20he%20doesn't%20expect%20another%20big%20year%20for%20returns%20like%20in%202023%20and%20so%20far%20in%202024%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20delivering%20gains%20of%2024%25%20and%2022%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Detrick%20said%20that%20the%20average%20gain%20of%20a%20bull%20market%20in%20year%20three%20is%20about%208%25%2C%20which%20is%20right%20around%20the%20average%20annual%20return%20for%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20in%20all%2C%20we%20expect%20stocks%20to%20be%20up%20at%20least%20low%20double%20digits%20over%20the%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Detrick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271148928-7cd9-413b-8146-f7a06f2d41cb%5C%22%3EBaird%2C%20Ross%20Mayfield%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBaird%20investment%20strategist%20Ross%20Mayfield%20said%20the%20third%20year%20of%20this%20current%20bull%20rally%20could%20deliver%20stronger%20returns%20than%20history%20suggests%20because%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20the%20bull%20delivered%20underwhelming%20performance%20relative%20to%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20two%20years%20of%20this%20bull%20market%20have%20been%20somewhat%20muted%20vs.%20historical%20standards%2C%20so%20there%20is%20ample%20opportunity%20for%20outperformance%20of%20the%20typical%20year%203%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayfield%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMayfield%20also%20echoed%20Detrick's%20sentiment%20that%20the%20average%20bull%20market%20is%20over%20five%20years%20long%2C%20so%20he%20thinks%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20plenty%20of%20room%20to%20run.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20not%20be%20surprising%20if%20year%20three%20of%20the%20bull%20market%20outperformed%20the%20typical%20year%20three%20given%20the%20rates%20backdrop%2C%20expected%20earnings%20growth%2C%20and%20tepid%20investor%20sentiment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayfield%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d92eafcb-b184-4d6f-927a-142734817da9%5C%22%3EUS%20Bank%20Asset%20Management%2C%20Rob%20Haworth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestment%20strategist%20Rob%20Haworth%20of%20US%20Bank%20Asset%20Management%20believes%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20surge%20to%206%2C480%20in%20its%20third%20year%20of%20the%20bull%20market%2C%20representing%20potential%20upside%20of%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaworth's%20bullish%20view%20is%20backed%20by%20what%20really%20drives%20stock%20prices%20higher%3A%20earnings%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20forward%20metric%20for%20market%20returns%20remains%20the%20pace%20of%20earnings%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Haworth%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20look%20ahead%2C%20we%20still%20see%20a%20constructive%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaworth%20expects%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20to%20deliver%20%24270%20in%20earnings%20per%20share%20next%20year%2C%20representing%20about%2013%25%20growth%20from%202024%20consensus%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLower%20interest%20rates%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20and%20soft%20or%20no-landing%20economic%20scenarios%20are%20helping%20lift%20growth%20into%20next%20year%2C%20supporting%20further%20equity%20market%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20Haworth%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-bull-rally-anniversary-earnings