ships-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoblox%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20under%20attack%20this%20week%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Froblox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20prominent%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20accused%20it%20of%20inflating%20user%20numbers%20and%20failing%20to%20protect%20children%20from%20predators.%20The%20gaming%20platform's%20stock%20temporarily%20dropped%20about%2010%25%20following%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20is%20a%20forensic%20research%20firm%20that%20makes%20money%20by%20betting%20against%20companies%20it%20targets%20and%20benefiting%20from%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission's%20whistleblower%20program.%20It's%20published%20reports%20on%20other%20tech%20companies%20that%20have%20led%20to%20SEC%20investigations%20and%20indictments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20investors%20seem%20to%20have%20largely%20shrugged%20off%20this%20report.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-not-allowed-my-child-kids-why-explained-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoblox%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock%20closed%20at%20%2441.60%20on%20Friday%2C%20slightly%20above%20where%20it%20was%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%20when%20Hindenberg%20published%20its%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20face%2C%20the%20report%20sounds%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETitled%20%26quot%3BRoblox%3A%20Inflated%20Key%20Metrics%20For%20Wall%20Street%20And%20A%20Pedophile%20Hellscape%20For%20Kids%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20accused%20the%20gaming%20platform%20popular%20with%20kids%20of%20inflating%20its%20user%20numbers%20in%20public%20reports%20by%2025%25%20to%2042%25%20by%20counting%20multiple%20accounts%20held%20by%20the%20same%20person.%20It%20claimed%20bots%20are%20%26quot%3Brampant%20on%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20inflate%20its%20user%20counts.%20It%20also%20renewed%20criticisms%20that%20Roblox%20had%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20lack%20of%20su