EChild-safety%20claims%20about%20Roblox%20similar%20to%20those%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20had%20also%20already%20been%20documented%20in%20places%20like%20Bloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2024-roblox-pedophile-problem%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusinessweek%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20published%20a%20wide-ranging%20investigation%20on%20the%20subject%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20there%20was%20a%20pedophile%20problem%20and%20scams%20in%20Roblox%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ron%20Kerbs%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20online%20child%20safety%20company%20Kidas.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20an%20'I%20told%20you%20so'%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6886112-ac24-4da9-88b6-e745771a7298%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20could%20hinder%20Roblox's%20ad%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Roblox's%20nearly%20immediate%20stock%20recovery%20and%20support%20from%20Wall%20Street%2C%20the%20report%20and%20related%20issues%20could%20have%20implications%20for%20Roblox's%20advertising%20business.%20Its%20ad%20business%20is%20barely%20a%20rounding%20error%20today%2C%20but%20Roblox%20is%20still%20not%20profitable%2C%20so%20it's%20trying%20hard%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-companies-that-help-advertisers-reach-gamers-without-annoying-them-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdvertisers%20increasingly%20recognize%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiscord-grow-ad-business-video-format-ipo-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue%20of%20games%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Roblox's%20pitch%20is%20that%20it%20reaches%20a%20highly%20engaged%20audience%20of%20hard-to-reach%20young%20people.%20In%20February%2C%20it%20reported%2071.5%20million%20daily%20active%20users%2C%2058%25%20of%20whom%20were%20over%2013.%20Walmart%2C%20Warner%20Bros.%20Pictures%2C%20and%20E.l.f.%20