0Johnson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67084869a7031864928112cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Jovan%20Johnson.%3Cp%3EJovan%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20financial%20planner%2C%20I%20know%20overcoming%20anxiety%20over%20money%20is%20essential%20for%20young%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20practical%20step%20is%20simply%20making%20sure%20you%20plan%20ahead%20with%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20it's%20essential%20that%20you%20give%20yourself%20grace%20and%20don't%20compare%20yourself%20to%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20rising%20costs%2C%20stagnant%20salaries%2C%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20social%20media%2C%20financial%20anxiety%20among%20young%20adults%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high.%20Financial%20anxiety%20can%20manifest%20as%20worry%20about%20paying%20bills%2C%20fear%20for%20the%20economy%2C%20a%20desire%20to%20avoid%20checking%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-banks%5C%22%3Ebank%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hoarding%20cash%2C%20and%20being%20overly%20cautious%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-are-the-best-investment-apps%5C%22%3Einvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6966650%2Fmoney-stress-illness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETime%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20is%20growing%20evidence%20linking%20financial%20anxiety%20to%20negative%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20outcomes.%20Addressing%20this%20anxiety%20is%20critical%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20for%20your%20overall%20well-being%20but%20also%20for%20achieving%20greater%20financial%20stability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20financial%20planner%2C%20I%20have%20five%20ways%20young%20adults%20can%20overcome%20their%20financial%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Plan%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinancially%20challenging%20times%20are%20inevitable%2C%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20job%20loss%2C%20medical%20emergency%2C%20or%20another%20unexpected%20event.%20One%20way%20to%20reduce%20financial%20anxiety%20about%20the%20future%20is%20by%20planning%20ahead.%20This%20includes%20building%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sinking%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20emergency%20fund%20provides%20a%20financial%20cushion%20that%20can%20ease%20your%20anxiety%20about%20the%20unknown.%20I%20recommend%20automating%20savings%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ehigh-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20you%20reach%20three%20to%2012%20months'%20worth%20of%20expenses%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20risk%20tolerance.%20One%20of%20my%20favorite%20options%20for%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fsofi-checking-savings-review%5C%22%3ESoFi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20have%20multiple%20savings%20accounts%20for%20your%20sinking%20funds%20and%20emergency%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESinking%20funds%20are%20also%20key%20to%20giving%20you%20peace%20of%20mind.%20These%20are%20savings%20accounts%20set%20aside%20for%20specific%20goals%2C%20such%20as%20travel%2C%20medical%20expenses%2C%20or%20car%20maintenance.%20I%20suggest%20keeping%20these%20sinking%20funds%20in%20the%20same%20bank%20as%20your%20emergency%20fund%20for%20convenience.%20Many%20online%20banks%20allow%20multiple%20savings%20accounts%20for%20different%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Find%20a%20place%20that%20brings%20you%20peace%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20all%20we%20need%20is%20a%20change%20of%20environment%20to%20feel%20less%20anxious%20about%20our%20finances.%20Find%20a%20place%20that%20brings%20you%20peace%2C%20where%20you%20can%20focus%20on%20addressing%20your%20financial%20situation%20without%20distractions.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20minimize%20added%20stress%20in%20your%20surroundings%20when%20you%20sit%20down%20to%20manage%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20quiet%2C%20calm%20space%20can%20help%20you%20be%20more%20productive%20and%20confident%20in%20your%20financial%20decisions.%20The%20key%20is%20to%20find%20what%20works%20for%20you%20and%20fosters%20the%20mindset%20needed%20to%20take%20meaningful%20steps%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Stop%20comparing%20yourself%20to%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20world%2C%20it%20feels%20almost%20impossible%20not%20to%20compare%20ourselves%20to%20others.%20Whether%20through%20social%20media%20or%20reality%20TV%2C%20we%20are%20constantly%20bombarded%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20versions%26quot%3B%20of%20others'%20lives.%20We%20see%20our%20peers%20going%20on%20trips%20or%20buying%20things%20we%20can't%20afford%2C%20which%20only%20feeds%20into%20our%20financial%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20remember%2C%20much%20of%20what%20we%20see%20isn't%20real.%20Many%20people%20who%20project%20a%20%26quot%3Bluxury%26quot%3B%20lifestyle%20are%20dealing%20with%20the%20same%20financial%20anxieties%20and%20struggles%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20take%20breaks%20from%20these%20sources%20of%20comparison.%20Focus%20on%20your%20own%20journey%20and%20your%20current%20financial%20situation.%20Create%20a%20plan%20that%20works%20for%20you%20to%20reduce%20financial%20anxiety.%20Everyone's%20path%20is%20different%2C%20and%20that's%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Give%20yourself%20grace%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20habit%20to%20reduce%20financial%20anxiety%20is%20giving%20yourself%20grace.%20Life%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20lived%20and%20enjoyed%2C%20even%20while%20managing%20finances.%20Find%20ways%20to%20celebrate%20your%20progress%20along%20the%20journey.%20Have%20you%20saved%20one%20month%20of%20expenses%20for%20your%20emergency%20fund%3F%20Reward%20yourself!%20Don't%20let%20financial%20anxiety%20stop%20you%20from%20living%20your%20life.%20Tackle%20your%20money%20worries%20one%20day%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20remember%20to%20enjoy%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Reach%20out%20for%20support%20and%20educate%20yourself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20to%20go%20through%20this%20journey%20alone.%20Many%20others%20are%20experiencing%20or%20have%20experienced%20similar%20financial%20struggles.%20Building%20a%20support%20system%20is%20crucial%20to%20keep%20you%20moving%20forward.%20Life%20can%20be%20tough%2C%20but%20it%20becomes%20easier%20when%20we%20face%20it%20together%20instead%20of%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20many%20free%20resources%20available%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20managing%20money.%20Financial%20anxiety%20often%20stems%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20education.%20The%20more%20knowledgeable%20you%20become%20about%20finances%2C%20the%20more%20empowered%20you%20will%20feel%20to%20take%20control%20of%20your%20financial%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%