ducation%2C%20Action%20and%20Research%20in%20Community%20Health)%20and%20have%20spent%20three%20decades%20working%20with%20tribal%20communities%20in%20Gadchiroli%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20couple%20isn%E2%80%99t%20lauded%20simply%20for%20their%20inventive%20take%20on%20tribal%20healthcare%2C%20but%20also%20their%20culturally%20appropriate%20approaches.%20In%20a%20region%20where%20language%2C%20culture%20barriers%2C%20and%20geographic%20inaccessibility%20pose%20significant%20challenges%2C%20and%20illness%20is%20often%20understood%20through%20spiritual%20beliefs%20and%20traditional%20healing%20practices%2C%20introducing%20modern%20medicine%20required%20thoughtful%20and%20respectful%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20tribes%E2%80%99%20reluctance%20melted%20into%20gratitude%2C%20the%20Bangs%20knew%20they%20were%20on%20the%20right%20path.%20Thirty-nine%20years%20ago%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20the%20premier%20Johns%20Hopkins%2C%20they%20stood%20at%20the%20precipice%20of%20a%20sea%20of%20opportunities%2C%20each%20more%20lucrative%20than%20the%20other.%20But%2C%20an%20inner%20voice%20guided%20their%20next%20step%20%E2%80%94%20research%20is%20fruitful%20in%20areas%20where%20problems%20exist%2C%20not%20where%20facilities%20are%20ample.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20formed%20the%20backbone%20of%20their%20decision%20to%20head%20to%20the%20naxal-hit%2C%20Maoist%20Gadchiroli%20in%20Maharashtra.%20And%20their%20arrival%20was%20interpreted%20as%20a%20blessing.%20Since%20the%20outset%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20attempted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338010%2Fkerala-startup-mykare-building-uber-of-healthcare-for-surgeries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eachieve%20health%20equity%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20relegating%20reductive%20healthcare%20to%20the%20boot%20and%20bringing%20in%20scientific%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5