7-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368497%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20integration%20of%20smart%20TVs%20in%20classrooms%20in%20collaboration%20with%20LEAD%20Group%2C%20academics%20is%20no%20longer%20limited%20to%20the%20textbook.%20Teacher%20Divya%E2%80%99s%20classroom%20is%20one%20example%20of%20this%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20smart%20TVs%20in%20classrooms%2C%20digital%20tablets%20with%20pre-loaded%20lesson%20plans%20and%20tools%20for%20teachers%2C%20and%20school%20excellence%20kits%20that%20couple%20audio-visual%20learning%20with%20a%20kinesthetic%20approach%2C%20the%20duo%20is%20certain%20that%20learning%20is%20set%20to%20touch%20new%20horizons.%20Head%20Nandan%20testifies%20to%20this.%20%E2%80%9CA%20smart%20and%20interactive%20learning%20environment%20is%20created%20for%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20loving%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes!%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Tanushree%2C%20a%20primary%20student.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20particularly%20thrilled%20as%20her%20favourite%20fable%20%E2%80%98Magic%20Pot%E2%80%99%20got%20a%20whole%20new%20meaning%20through%20the%20audio-visual%20content.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20see%20everything%20that%20is%20in%20my%20textbook%20and%20also%20watch%20it%20happening!%20I%20love%20learning%20phonics%2C%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sumeet%20and%20Smita%20set%20out%20to%20transform%20the%20educational%20landscape%20in%20India%20with%20an%20ambition%20to%20reshape%20classroom%20dynamics%2C%20their%20focus%20lay%20on%20tier%20two%2C%20three%2C%20and%20four%20towns.%20And%20this%20calculated%20decision%20has%20been%20rewarding.%20Today%2C%20LEAD%20Group%20is%20present%20in%20over%208%2C000%20schools%2C