ificant%20traction%2C%20with%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20in%20the%20previous%20financial%20year.%20Every%20month%2C%20the%20startup%20utilises%20up%20to%20600%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264157%2Fbanana-fibre-earns-lakhs-waste-business-success-ecofriendly-handicraft%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanana%20fibres%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20waste.%20Through%20offline%20and%20online%20marketing%2C%20it%20has%20established%20its%20customer%20base%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20also%20converts%20leftover%20pulp%20from%20the%20fibre%20extraction%20into%20vermicompost%20and%20liquid%20fertiliser.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20also%20converts%20leftover%20pulp%20from%20the%20fibre%20extraction%20into%20vermicompost%20and%20liquid%20fertiliser.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2