lock-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20S%20P%20Shahi%3A%20The%20guardian%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20wolves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahuadanr%20Wolf%20Sanctuary%20in%20Jharkhand%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20sanctuary%20in%20India%20dedicated%20to%20wolf%20preservation%20%E2%80%94%20owes%20its%20existence%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300043%2Fforgotten-forest-officer-sp-shahi-behind-indias-only-wolf-sanctuary-mahuadanr-jharkhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%20P%20Shahi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20pioneering%20conservationist%20and%20forest%20officer.%20Back%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20he%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20how%20wolves%20were%20hurtling%20towards%20extinction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWildlife%20historian%20Raza%20Kazmi%20noted%20how%20unlike%20most%20forest%20officers%20of%20his%20era%2C%20Shahi%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20what%20we%20now%20call%20%E2%80%98Open%20Natural%20Ecosystems%E2%80%99%20for%20wolves.%20These%20ecosystems%20consist%20of%20a%20range%20of%20non-forested%20habitats%20from%20savanna%20grasslands%20to%20deserts%2C%20which%20host%20a%20high%20density%20of%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20mammalian%20fauna%E2%80%9D.%20What%E2%80%99s%20particularly%20interesting%20about%20these%20ecosystems%20is%20that%20unlike%20wildlife%20sanctuaries%20and%20other%20protected%20areas%20where%20limits%20are%20set%20on%20human%20habitation%2C%20they%20support%20the%20lives%20and%20livelihoods%20of%20pastoralists%20and%20their%20livestock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FSP-Shahi-Mahuadanr-Wolves-Feature-Image-2-1665669212.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SP%20Shahi%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Indian%20grey%20wolf%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%