become%20a%20%E2%80%98free-living%20family%20member%E2%80%99%20at%20Choudhury%E2%80%99s%20official%20bungalow%20in%20Jashipur.%20She%20was%20fed%20with%20mutton%20and%20milk%20powder%2C%20slept%20on%20their%20beds%20and%20often%20played%20with%20them.%20Saroj%20closely%20observed%20her%20to%20study%20the%20various%20behavioural%20aspects%20of%20tigers%2C%20especially%20the%20use%20of%20pheromones%2C%20their%20mating%20behaviour%20and%20territoriality%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20long%20before%20Saroj%20Raj%20Choudhury%20took%20over%20as%20the%20Simlipal%20Tiger%20Reserve%E2%80%99s%20first%20Field%20Director%20and%20met%20Khairi%2C%20he%20had%20already%20established%20himself%20as%20a%20pioneer%20of%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20particularly%20of%20tigers%2C%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20developing%20the%20pugmark%20tracking%20technique%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20the%20bedrock%20of%20organising%20tiger%20censuses%20in%20India%20till%202004%20and%20the%20foundation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20much%20vaunted%20Project%20Tiger%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20to%20mentoring%20generations%20of%20forest%20officers%20in%20the%20finer%20nuances%20of%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20Choudhury%20remains%20a%20legendary%20conservationist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F17145020%2FSaroj-Raj-Choudury-12.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saroj%20Raj%20Choudhury%20with%20Khairi%20%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-233089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaroj%20Raj%20Choudhury%20with%20Khairi%20(Image%20courtesy%20Twitter%2FRamesh%20Pandey%20IFS)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFateh_Singh_Rathore%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWikimedia%20Commons%2FFateh%20Singh%20Rathore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSanctuaryAsia%2Fstatus%2F956436281835360256%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%2FSanctuary%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amit%20Sankhala%2C%20SLC-IT%2C%20Raza%20Kazmi%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Frameshpandeyifs%2Fstatus%2F1282671780729982977%3Fs%3D19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%2FRamesh%20Pandey%20IFS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728031345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05103523%2FFateh_Singh_Rathore_2008-500x693.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D368687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20snow%20leopard%20conservationist%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20to%20tiger%20protection%20pioneer%20Kailash%20Sankhala%2C%20these%20individuals%20fought%20to%20protect%20endangered%20species%2C%20inspire%20community-based%20conservation%2C%20and%20challenge%20systemic%20threats.%20Their%20legacies%20continue%20shaping%20India's%20conservation%20efforts%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368687%2Fworld-animal-welfare-day-remembering-pioneers-wildlife-conservation-india-project-tiger%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Family%20Brought%20The%20300-YO%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20Back%20to%20Life%20As%20a%20Heritage%20Site%20%26amp%3B%20Hotel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20palace%20was%20overgrown%20with%20brambles%3B%20the%20manor%20barely%20visible%20through%20the%20forests%20that%20threatened%20to%20suffocate%20it.%20Even%20the%20highest%20points%20of%20the%20castle%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20spared.%20Wild%20plants%20held%20the%20towers%20in%20a%20vice-like%20grip.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20roof%20had%20crumbled%3B%20in%20others%20it%20had%20shattered%2C%20closing%20off%20entrances%20and%20exits.%20No%20one%20knew%20for%20sure%20what%20the%20house%20held%20within%20it.%20Were%20there%20wild%20beasts%20lurking%20inside%3F%20Or%20something%20more%20ferocious%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20it%20sounds%20like%20an%20excerpt%20from%20one%20of%20Grimm%E2%80%99s%20Fairy%20Tales%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20real-life%20scene%20that%20awaited%20Pallab%20Roy%20(60)%20and%20his%20family%20when%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310006%2Froyal-sisters-duo-akshita-mrinalika-the-belgadia-palace-boutique-hotel-odisha-sustainable-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevisited%20their%20ancestral%20palace%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kasim%20Bazar%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20300-year-old%20architecture%20had%20fallen%20into%20a%20state%20of%20despair%20since%20its%20last%20occupant%2C%20Pallab%E2%80%99s%20grandfather%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%2C%20passed%20away%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallab%20has%20my%20unwavering%20attention%20as%20he%20narrates%20his%20story%2C%20a%20tale%20that%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20an%20Enid%20Blyton%20adventure.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20his%20parents%20Prosanta%20Kumar%20and%20Supriya%20Roy%2C%20his%20wife%20Sudeshna%2C%20his%20son%20Saurav%2C%20and%20his%20daughter-in-law%20Priya%2C%20would%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20take%20upon%20them%20the%20arduous%20task%20of%20restoring%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20turn%20this%20spectral%20ruin%20into%20a%20liveable%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%3A%20Battling%20snakes%20and%20lizards%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20approaching%20one%20room%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20says%20as%20he%20recalls%20the%20renovation%20process.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20%E2%80%98operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%20commenced%20that%20the%20family%20could%20ascertain%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20devastation.%20The%20years%20of%20isolation%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20royal%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsects%2C%20five-inch%20thick%20layers%20of%20dust%20and%20crumbling%20roofs%20marred%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20restore%20what%20had%20once%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-goa-maharashtra-sawantwadi-palace-hotel-run-by-royal-family-sawant-bhonsle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymbol%20of%20grandeur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20was%20infested%20with%20snakes%20and%20monitor%20lizards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20exclaims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20is%20an%2018th%20century%20marvel%20in%20Murshidabad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F